{"tid":1492216,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"鯉魚門老字號茶餐廳 老闆娘堅定撐警：我到而家都仲撐警察","createTime":"2019-08-20T17:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T03:55:03.000Z","uid":51183,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dc4d3fe59a683f0b89fc53d4d048145f9602790d","tid":1492216,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:29:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/etw/magazine/article/20190820/3_59953974/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fetw%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190820%2F3_59953974%2F&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41LHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=896ad5bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fetw%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190820%2F3_59953974%2F&h=6bda9f97\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/etw/magazine/article/20190820/3_59953974/</a><br />\n<br />\n【逆權運動】鯉魚門老字號茶餐廳 老闆娘堅定撐警：我到而家都仲撐警察 <br />\n<br />\n鯉魚門開業五十多年的銀龍咖啡茶座，過往以獨創腐乳多士及懷舊氣氛聞名，最近就因老闆娘Kate撐警，在撐警集會中主動上台表態支持的立場，惹起不少網民評論。<br />\n<br />\n食評網站上，本地食客及內地網民因Kate立場而展開對罵，Kate在接受其他傳媒採訪時，一方面表明堅定立場，一方面表示最近有不少客人上門支持她，認定自己沒有做錯。<br />\n<br />\n在8月20日，有警員涉及向長者施以酷刑的閉路電視片段被廣傳，引來全城嘩然。在此情況下，到底Kate立場會否有改變﹖記者到訪茶餐廳時，Kate正接受新華社採訪，而她得知記者是蘋果日報旗下員工後，拒絕接受訪問，但在電話訪問中，Kate仍認為警察沒有做錯﹕「我撐好警察。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有好警察咩？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d47fcb162a8591b7ea456ac51401e6823020eed","tid":1492216,"uid":95499,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:31:49.000Z","msg":"唔好再同佢免費宣傳好冇？"},{"pid":"fac75862461c6daf27d045efa5d2c3dce7b90cae","tid":1492216,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"188fddcebfcf4d653846bff495e379f